                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 5,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Flèche de givre"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Déchaînement élémentaire</span><br><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 1 pt de </span><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">DGT Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">, inflige </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">1 pt de DGT de perforation</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> à tous les personnages adverses en attente et invoque une </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">perle de glace</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/22/158750877/6b78c979575a782c1625dce67992cf90_1452699715884198891.png",
                "id": "talent79595",
                "key": "Baptême céleste",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Baptême céleste"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Invocation</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Phase finale</span> : <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 1 pt de</span> <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">DGT Cryo</span> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">et inflige 1 pt de</span> <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">DGT de perforation</span> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">à tous les personnages adverses en attente.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Nombre d'utilisations : 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/22/158750877/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5196631861269389403.png",
                "id": "talent57916",
                "key": "Perle de glace",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/22/158750877/5768b83a04afeb8e581b0f7864fd39d9_6744082817104963978.png",
                "title": "Perle de glace"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Applique l'élément Cryo et peut déclencher les réactions élémentaires :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fonte </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DGT actuels +2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Supraconduction </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DGT actuels +1 et inflige 1 pt de DGT de perforation à tous les personnages adverses autres que la cible</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Gel </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DGT actuels +1 et immobilise la cible pendant la manche actuelle (Peut être annulé en avance en subissant des DGT physiques ou Pyro, mais DGT +2)</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/22/158750877/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_6746052156762263187.png",
                "id": "talent32765",
                "key": "DGT Cryo",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "DGT Cryo"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">DGT physiques</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Les DGT physiques n'appliquent aucun élément et ne peuvent pas non plus déclencher de réactions élémentaires.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">DGT de perforation</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Les DGT de perforation ne peuvent être augmentés par aucun bonus, mais ne peuvent pas non plus être bloqués par l'utilisation de boucliers ou d'immunités aux DGT.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Nombre d'utilisation</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Après le déclenchement de l'effet de cette carte, 1 de ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">est consommée.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Une carte est immédiatement défaussée une fois toutes ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">épuisées.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/22/158750877/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8016771072982167773.png",
